high_descs: Turn right, then right again to face a green trash-can and stove.
Pick up copper pot from stove.
Turn around and walk to the fridge.
Open the fridge, put the copper pot inside, close it, open it, take out the copper pot, and close the fridge.
Turn around and walk to the stove.
Place copper pot on top of stove.
anns.task_desc: Take a pot from the stove to the fridge.

high_descs: walk over to the kitchen stove
pick up the pan off of the stove
open the door of the fridge and put the pan inside the fridge, let it cool then take it out again
walk back over to the stove again
put the pan on the stove where you originally picked it up
anns.task_desc: cool the pan on top of the stove

high_descs: Pick up the left pan from the stove.
Bring the pan to the fridge.
chill the pan in the fridge for a few seconds.
Bring the pan back to the stove.
Put the pan back on the stove.
anns.task_desc: Chill the large pan in the fridge.
